Package: cultevo
Title: Tools, Measures and Statistical Tests for Cultural Evolution
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2018-04-19
Authors@R: person("Kevin Stadler", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="a00425926@unet.univie.ac.at")
Description: This package provides tools, measures and statistical
    tests often used in the study of cultural evolution, in particular for
    measuring the compositionality of signaling systems as well as computing
    string and meaning distance matrices. It also provides an accurate
    implementation of Page's test for monotonicity of ranks.
URL: https://kevinstadler.github.io/cultevo/
BugReports: https://github.com/kevinstadler/cultevo/issues
